{"tid":1853233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海關檢懷疑假生產日期口罩　政府安排3千萬口罩供港","createTime":"2020-01-31T00:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T00:48:29.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84b8dbf4128e1257def53887e0704a139689560b","tid":1853233,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:17:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505736-20200130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505736-20200130.htm&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=d914905a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505736-20200130.htm&h=e684c074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505736-20200130.htm</a><br />\n本港市面口罩供應緊張，政府表示正陸續安排逾3千萬個口罩供應私人市場。至於能否僅限港人或容許港人優先購買，政府則認為執行有困難。<br />\n<br />\n海關在旺角一間藥房拘捕一名負責人，涉嫌違反商品說明條例，出售生產日期為2020年3月的一批口罩，涉及數量超過6萬個。"},{"pid":"7cc55657955e56c7605041997dc563cb243e8e09","tid":1853233,"uid":124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"私人市場買 關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"5f717b4f40eb5bee5f552394aa413ffb29c599bf","tid":1853233,"uid":277888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:48:29.000Z","msg":"海關搜刮民脂以己用"}]}